---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTAButton from "../components/CTAButton.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="New Rider — TT Motorcycle School"
  description="New to motorcycles? Our one-hour New Rider course gives you private, off-road tuition with a DVSA instructor — ideal before your CBT. Based in Sussex."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section__eyebrow">New Rider Course</span>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">Your First Hour on a Bike</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__sub">
        A one-to-one introduction to motorcycling — no group pressure, no
        experience needed. Just you, an instructor, and a safe place to start.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-grid">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>What Is the New Rider Course?</h2>
        <p>
          Our New Rider course is a <strong
            >one hour lesson with a qualified DVSA instructor</strong
          >. Training takes place on a secure off-road area with no pressure of
          having to perform in front of a group of strangers — very important if
          you are at all nervous or anxious about riding a motorcycle for the
          first time.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you have little or no previous motorcycle experience, we cannot
          recommend strongly enough the value of this course.
        </p>

        <h2>Why Do This Before Your CBT?</h2>
        <p>
          The CBT is a full day of training and assessment. Coming in with even
          one hour of experience makes a real difference — you'll feel more
          comfortable on the bike, more confident with the controls, and more
          able to focus on what the instructor is teaching.
        </p>
        <p>
          Many riders who start with our New Rider course find their CBT day
          goes much more smoothly as a result.
        </p>

        <h2>What's Included?</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>One hour of private, one-to-one tuition</li>
          <li>Use of a motorcycle suitable for your size and experience</li>
          <li>Motorcycle safety clothing and helmet provided</li>
          <li>Fully qualified DVSA instructor throughout</li>
          <li>Training on a private, off-road site — no traffic</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What Comes Next?</h2>
        <p>
          After your New Rider session, the natural next step is your <a
            href="/cbt/">CBT (Compulsory Basic Training)</a
          > — the legal requirement to ride on UK roads. From there, you can work
          towards your <a href="/full-licence/">full motorcycle licence</a>.
          We'll be with you every step of the way.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar__card">
          <h3 class="sidebar__title">Ready to Book?</h3>
          <p class="sidebar__body">
            New Rider sessions are one-to-one and fill up quickly. Secure your
            spot today.
          </p>
          <CTAButton
            href="/cbtbooking/"
            label="Book Your Session"
            variant="accent"
            size="md"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar__card sidebar__card--plain">
          <h3 class="sidebar__title">Useful Links</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar__links">
            <li><a href="/cbt/">About CBT</a></li>
            <li><a href="/full-licence/">Full Licence Courses</a></li>
            <li><a href="/what-to-wear/">What to Wear</a></li>
            <li><a href="/prices/">View Prices</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact/">Ask a Question</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-10);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    }
  }

  .sidebar__card {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .sidebar__card--plain {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .sidebar__title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .sidebar__body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: #ccc;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .sidebar__links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .sidebar__links a {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .sidebar__links a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .prose a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
